Fix refactoring UnusedOperation

@funs_with_return_values has to be `nil` to mean "all of the functions".

Refs #594

Reimplement check with a blacklist of modules and a reduce

Check any calls following Map.get for membership in
@unsafe_modules.  Also implement new test.

Allow regexes in lint attributes

This provides a way to e.g. deactivate all Refactor checks:

    @lint [{~r/Refactor/, false}]
